-- Foxconn to Move `Major' Production to Hebei From Shenzhen, Newspaper Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-01T23:36:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/foxconn-to-move-major-production-to-hebei-from-shenzhen-newspaper-says.html

          
          
             Foxconn Technology Group will move a
“major part” of its production to Hebei province in northern
China from the southern city of Shenzhen by the end of this
year, Shanghai Daily reported today, citing company spokesman
Tong Wenxin.  
